93
00:03:35,559 --> 00:03:36,520
He wanted to ask you out for a drink.

94
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:37,479
I'm busy.

95
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:38,600
Well,

96
00:03:38,679 --> 00:03:39,440
Mr. Liang said

97
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,720
both of you are single

98
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,399
so you need some opportunities

99
00:03:41,399 --> 00:03:42,279
to meet some girls.

100
00:03:42,279 --> 00:03:43,360
Tonight,

101
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,839
he asked his friend
to invite some professors,

102
00:03:44,839 --> 00:03:45,800
stewardesses, and doctors over.

103
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,440
Every one of them is very good-looking.

104
00:03:48,279 --> 00:03:49,440
I've told you I don't have time.

105
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,160
I'm busy.

106
00:03:50,559 --> 00:03:51,839
Tell him, leave me alone

107
00:03:51,839 --> 00:03:52,600
