122
00:04:17,359 --> 00:04:18,480
You've come to the right person.

123
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,760
The trick is to ignore her rejection and never give up.

124
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,480
Is that so?

125
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:29,440
